<h2>Service Finalized 🎉</h2>
<p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>Great news! Your service <strong>{{serviceName}}</strong> has been completed and finalized by our team.</p>

<div class="details-box">
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Service</span>
    <span class="value">{{serviceName}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Reference ID</span>
    <span class="value">{{referenceId}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Status</span>
    <span class="value" style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 700;">Completed ✓</span>
  </div>
</div>

{{#if certificateUrl}}
<p>Your completion certificate is ready for download.</p>
<a href="{{certificateUrl}}" class="btn">Download Certificate</a>
{{else}}
<p>Your documents are available on your dashboard.</p>
<a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
{{/if}}

<p>Thank you for choosing DoorstepFilings. We look forward to serving you again!</p>
